data.description: This beautiful well maintained home has hardwood and tile flooring, granite countertops, wood burning fireplace on the carport which is setup to cook over the open flames. New HVAC 2022, new guttering with Leafguard lifetime warranty, new lighting indoor and out, new awning over side door, new storm door, new plumbing in bonus rm/den 1/2 acre of privacy fence in back, grinder under the house and lovely landscaping as well!  Storage bldg/garage remain, and the flooring in the unattached garage has new limestone added.
